sequenceDiagram
    participant UIRoot as UIRootUICtrl
    participant Res as ResManager
    participant SDK as SDKAdapter
    participant SDKImpl as HLDDZ/App/Web SDK
    participant Net as HttpManager
    participant PM as PlayerManager
    participant UI as UIController/UIManager
    participant Login as UILoginUICtrl
    participant Main as UIMainUICtrl

    UIRoot->>Res: parsePkg() 加载 Bundle/资源
    Res-->>UIRoot: 进度/完成(resState=true)
    UIRoot->>SDK: loadSDK() 选择实现并 setSDK()
    UIRoot->>SDK: HLDDZ_requestAuth(cb)
    SDK->>SDKImpl: 请求授权
    SDKImpl-->>SDK: rspRequestAuth(result, sessionKey, userid, ...)
    SDK-->>UIRoot: 授权回调(sdkState=true)

    UIRoot->>SDK: HLDDZ_getPlayerProfile(cb)
    SDK-->>UIRoot: 回包(同步 PM.HLDDZ_user 等)
    UIRoot->>SDK: HLDDZ_queryViewableAdCount(cb)

    UIRoot->>UIRoot: if (sdkState && resState) checkLogin()
    alt Web/调试：展示登录
      UIRoot->>UI: 打开 UIName.UILogin
      Login->>Net: POST Login
      Net-->>Login: token + role
      Login->>Net: GET Stage(max_stage)
      Net-->>Login: max_stage
      Login->>UI: 进入主界面 或 首关
    else 直进流程
      UIRoot->>Net: GET Stage(max_stage)
      Net-->>UIRoot: max_stage
      UIRoot->>UI: 有分享 extraStr → 直接进入分享对局
      UIRoot->>UI: 否则 打开主界面
    end

